text:
Good morning...
Did I make it on time?

Good morning, Mamimi.
Don't worry, there's still 5 minutes until the time we agreed on.

Oh what's this? Mamimin...
It's rare for your hair to be down isn't it? It's suuuper cute～!

No kidding～!
Just letting your hair down really gives off a different feel～!

Yes, the moment that you came into the office
I thought I had glimpsed a nobelwoman from a distant land.

For real! What happened today?  A change of heart?
Or did you actually come here to try and make us fall for you perhaps?

...It was nothing really...
There just wasn't time to style it is all.
Aren't you all making too big of a deal about this?

No... I also...
thought... it was cute...
